{"_path":"/fitness/f019","_dir":"fitness","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"瑜珈 - 熱瑜伽","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":19,"category":"瑜珈運動","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-10-15T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"瑜珈-熱瑜伽"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"瑜珈 - 熱瑜伽"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"reference"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reference"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.trueyogafitness.com.tw/Classes/GroupCourse.aspx?id=6"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"熱瑜伽"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.worldgymtaiwan.com/tag/%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95/%E7%86%B1%E7%91%9C%E7%8F%883%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"爆汗熱瑜珈排毒減重 但要注意 3 大運動風險！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r3nq15XsrC0"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"熱瑜伽 26 式序列"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6XnN_fqiEP0"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"50 分鐘 溫和瑜伽"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":""},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":""},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"熱瑜伽簡介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"熱瑜伽簡介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"熱瑜珈起源"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n熱瑜珈是由印度瑜珈大師 Bikram Choudhury 在美國帶領風潮，故又名 Bikram Yoga，一套共 26 式及 2 個呼吸式，屬於中強度柔韌性運動；它模擬瑜珈起源地印度的炎熱和潮濕的運動環境，讓大家在溫暖的環境裏練習瑜珈可更快地發熱。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"熱瑜珈特色"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n模擬起源地的環境，可貼近最初期練習瑜珈者的身心狀態，最大的特色是在 #攝氏 38 到 41 度的高溫、#40%~50%的溼度 環境下完成整套動作，讓瑜珈的效力從人體中自然爆發出來，直接刺激神經和肌肉系統，這不只讓肌肉伸展度更好，還能促進血液循環、增加新陳代謝、刺激淋巴系統將毒素排出等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"熱瑜伽-26-式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"熱瑜伽 26 式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"熱瑜珈是由這 26 個姿勢所組成，每個動作都約莫停 3-5 個呼吸，這些都有一定的固定順序，會如此安排是因為每個瑜珈體位都是為下一個動作做暖身準備，當 26 個體位法都做完之後，身體的每個部位與每一塊肌肉，都會充實的被鍛鍊到了！也正因如此，熱瑜珈能讓肌肉均衡發展，避免腰酸背痛，而且其中幾個體位法，是為了強化脊椎與背部肌肉而設計，讓你到年長時都能抬頭挺胸。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f019-01.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f019-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"瑜珈-熱瑜伽","depth":2,"text":"瑜珈 - 熱瑜伽","children":[{"id":"reference","depth":3,"text":"Reference"},{"id":"熱瑜伽簡介","depth":3,"text":"熱瑜伽簡介"},{"id":"熱瑜伽-26-式","depth":3,"text":"熱瑜伽 26 式"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:fitness:f019.md","_source":"content","_file":"fitness/f019.md","_extension":"md"}